Our Mission
"Solutions for Americans from America’s Think Tank," reflects our goal to unleash the power of ideas for positive change by identifying, encouraging and aggressively marketing the best scholarly research and innovative solutions.  We work to educate the public, the media and policy makers about ways to create an opportunity economy for all Americans.
